{"tid":1400673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚示威者做啲咩，會影響8.5 罷工人數！","createTime":"2019-08-03T13:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T10:59:58.000Z","uid":282490,"like":117,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d64d52cd3eec633ec6a1299f84fe3cdd72f790fe","tid":1400673,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:34:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我唔該某班五毛/鬼唔好玩野<br />\n我知有智慧嘅勇武巴絲係唔會亂黎<br />\n<br />\n我係講緊果啲憑血氣做事嘅人（同埋鬼！）<br />\n<br />\n唔好怪我話果啲磨爛蓆唔撤嘅人係鬼<br />\n係人都知星期一係和理非回合<br />\n今晚兩日如果做左啲咩太「激進」<br />\n例如玩火、出港獨字眼等等<br />\n<br />\n係直接影響罷工人數<br />\n<br />\n中間派係港共中共積極爭取緊嘅群體<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">8.5 衰左，咁成場運動係即刻game over </span></span><br />\n<br />\n我唔該你地睇下現場有無人想破壞呢場運動（無啦啦激動又煽動人激動果啲）<br />\n<br />\n有咩唔該8.5 後先搞好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n </span>"},{"pid":"5dcd6d7d9521ff2d96e9f6f82458a66c43ead365","tid":1400673,"uid":241244,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:35:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"62b03aa981a93b38a5e0269a084d04830bc6e220","tid":1400673,"uid":282490,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:36:50.000Z","msg":"唔好睇唔起<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">一班和理非</span></span><br />\n<br />\n佢地有好多坐喺政府中上層，或者商界有話事權嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">係有牙力有影響力，可以影響成個局勢嘅人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一定要爭取佢地支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d04ee0edcd2073035d669f95de25ed9d1976cf","tid":1400673,"uid"